The paper focuses on investigating communication channels during safety analysis in industry, which is a software engineering activity. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. The paper also touches upon issues related to security and confidentiality, which can be related to cs.CY (Cryptography and Security).
